title: United Kingdom Imports - Works Of Art, Collectors' Pieces & Antiques
description: Imports - Works Of Art, Collectors' Pieces & Antiques in the United Kingdom increased to 338.60 GBP Million in September from 163.94 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Works Of Art, Collectors' Pieces & Antiq in the United Kingdom averaged 215.64 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 990.41 GBP Million in June of 2011 and a record low of -0.06 GBP Million in April of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Works of Art, Collectors Pieces & Ant.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
